  <brief_title>Utility of Disconnection Technique for One Lung Ventilation</brief_title>
  <official_title>Utility of Disconnection Technique for One Lung Ventilation: a Comparison of a Double Lumen Endobronchial Tube With a Bronchial Blocker</official_title>
